name: AI Imagined Pixel Art Painted by a Robot
description:
3 years ago I minted my first works on
SuperRare. They were AI portraits
painted by my robot after studying
10,000 celebrity faces. Wondered
what the same algorithm would do
with 10,000 CryptoPunks, and this is
the result. This experiment came out
of conversations with yeahyeah
(punk8116) as we wondered about
ways to incorporate the crypto
blockchain into portraiture. This is the
first of my portraits to be able to do
so, something that I have been trying
to figure out a way to do for years.
